				<td colspan="2"><span>I'm not a bard, but I did have a 65 ranger that did the quest up to and including the 8th ring for a good...sheesh...dozen people (MQ'd it with people in my guild)...so if people have questions, I'll check back here periodically. This was shortly after Luclin came out, and at that time I think I was the only one farming the quest (and sold a couple 8th ring MQ's for a hefty sum<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />) 
<br />

<br />
Anywho, important note: You can be doing multiple rings at the same time - IE, at one point I had 1st, 2nd, 3rd, 4th, 6th, and 7th rings on me...so while you're running around doing one of the later rings, keep collecting the stuff for the previous rings in case you blow it.
