				<td colspan="2"><span>If you're only concerned about part 2 right now, it is VERY easy if you just go an kill the 3 frost giants (captain and 2 other special ones) at the fortress before you start, and kill the (normal) Frost Giant and Ry'Gorr at the Ulthork camp in advance. Kill them, and then you don't have to worry about them later.
<br />

<br />
Another trick is to chain cast your Lull on the coldain you're escorting. It keeps him from attacking mobs that will kill him.
<br />

<br />
I did the first 8 ring quests at 60th lvl without any problems. Keep Rodrick's dagger and head from that piece, for the 9th, and you'll save yourself a later step.</span></td>
